
Your hot and fiery passionate side
Gift: You are indeed filled with a lot of intensity. You are a rare type that knows what you want and will go after it. Your passion allows you too examine qualities not only in yourself but others and it's not forget that bedroom passion you have.
Curse: That side of you also makes you somewhat crazy (to be blunt). You can become jealous, aggressive, temperamental, and unforgiving because of that passion.



